quran[7]{c,v,t}:
  4,95,"Havana kuenzana avo vanotenda vanogara (mudzimba) kusiya kweavo vasingakwanisi vakakuvara (mapofu nevakaremara), neavo vanhu vanotsungirira nekurwa munzira yaAllah nehupfumi hwavo nehupenyu hwavo. Allah vakave vanosimudzira muzvidanho avo vanhu vanotsungirira kurwa nehupfumi hwavo nehupenyu hwavo kune avo vanhu vanogara (kumba). Pane umwe, Allah vakamuvimbisa zvakanaka (Paradhiso), asi Allah vakasarudza avo vanotsungirira nekurwa kune avo vanogara (kumba) nemubairo mukuru"
  4,96,"Zvidanho zviri pamusoro kubva kwavari, nekuregererwa netsitsi. Uye Allah ndivo vanoregerera zvikuru, vane tsitsi zhinji"
  4,97,"Zvirokwazvo, avo ngirozi dzinotora moyo yavo vari pakati pekutadza pachezvavo (sekugara kwavanoita nevasingatendi nyangwe zvazvo kutama kwakave kunomanikidzirwa kwavari), (Ngirozi) dzinoti (kwavari): “Maive muri pachidanho chipi?” Vanopindura vachiti: “Tangatiri vanhu vakaneta uye taidzvanyirirwa panyika.” (Ngirozi) dzinoti: “Nyika yaAllah yange isina kufara here kwamuri kuti muve munotama mairi?” Vanhu vakadaro vachagara kuGehena. Uye inzvimbo yakashata kugara"
  4,98,"Kusiya kwevanhu vasina simba pakati pavo, varume, vakadzi nevana vasingakwanise kuronga, uye vasingakwanise kutsvaga imwe nzira"
  4,99,"Ava ndivo vanhu vacharegererwa naAllah, uye Allah ndivo vanokanganwira zvikuru, vanoregerera zvikuru"
  4,100,"Uye uyo anotama (kubva kumba kwake) munzira yaAllah, achawana nzvimbo dzakawanda dzekugara neraramo. Uye uyo anosiya imba yake achitama achienda kuna Allah nemutumwa wavo (Muhammad (SAW)), uye rufu romuwana, mubairo wake una Allah. Uye Allah ndivo vanoregerera zvikuru, vane tsitsi zhinji"
  4,101,"Uye pamunenge muri parwendo (maMuslim) munyika, hamuna chitadzo mukave munodimbura Swalaah (Munamato) kana muchitya kuti vanhu vasingatendi vangangokuisai pamiedzo (kukurwisai kana kukuitai zvimwe zvakaipa). Zvirokwazvo, vanhu vasingatendi imhandu dzenyu dziri pachena"